# About

This is task for job proposal from Adeo Web

## Usage

To start using the app run fixtures
To get forecast data run console command

```bash
php bin/console app:forecast
```

To access recommendations use this path:

```bash
/product/{city}
```

After loading fixtures two cities are available (Vilnius and Kaunas).

